==Malay==
===Pronoun===
'''daku'''
# [[I]], [[me]] 

used as an object for:
(i)a preposition before "aku" which ended with an 'n'.(eg. "akan" and "dengan"<br>
(ii)transitive verb before "aku" which ended with an 'n'.(eg. "menemankan" and "mementingkan".